4. David Cooper

# David Cooper

## Senior Systems Administrator HPC Large Scale Systems

Phone: **512-475-9404** |
Email: **[dcooper@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:dcooper@tacc.utexas.edu)**

David joined TACC in 2014, initially in the operations group, but became a systems administrator in 2016. He is currently a senior systems administrator focused primarily on storage systems. He manages the Stockyard or Lustre /work filesystem, an IBM ESS and TS4500 tape library, for replication of Corral, the DDN disk frontend of our Ranch tape archive, a WEKA all-flash filesystem for Frontera, and our license servers.

### Education

**B.S., Computer Science**  

Texas A&M University-Corpus Christi